parameters: \n<Comment>Damn, just her face is already too erotic.
\n<Streamer>Today, we have a special guest, the new model!
\n<Streamer>I mean, we have Eury-chan with us!
\n<Comment>I heard there's a naughty girl appearing.
\n<Streamer>So let's dive right into the question corner with Eury-chan!

\n<Streamer>Straight to the point, what does Eury-chan want to do in
Tengoku City?
\n<Eury>Of course, it's to fulfill the mission I've been given!
\n<Comment>The new model is brimming with enthusiasm, lol.

\n<Eury>Ah, but, well, maybe I do feel a little bit like playing
around.

\n<Eury>Since I left Marion-san's place to come here, I'm freer than
before.
\n<Streamer>Then, how about we go for a deep question!
\n<Streamer>Tell us about your favorite play, Eury-chan!
\n<Comment>This is going to be an epic episode.

\n<Eury>(What does she mean... Is she talking about my combat
style?)
\n<Eury>Well, I like to close the distance with my opponent and...
\n<Eury>(A sudden forced kiss!? And on stream!?))
\n<Eury>(She's licking every corner of my mouth, gross...!)
\n<Streamer>How about it? You like this kind of thing?
\n<Eury>I wasn't informed about this kind of thing!

\n<Streamer>Come on, it's fine. You said earlier that you wanted to
fulfill your mission, right?
\n<Eury>This is not part of the mission!

\n<Eury>This is sexual harassment! This is definitely sexual
harassment!

\n<Streamer>Since Eury-chan is quite upset, shall we cut the stream here
for today?
\n<Streamer>So, as a final gift to the viewers!
\n<Streamer>Eury-chan, please say the closing greeting to the camera!
\n<Eury>Well then... thank you for your hard work.

\n<Streamer>The closing greeting has to be in the proper Tengatsu TV
style~!
\n<Streamer>You have to say it properly or we can't end the stream~?
\n<Streamer>To all the viewers, otsunpo tsun tsu-n!
\n<Eury>Everything about this is wrong! I'm not coming back!
\n<Streamer>Look, I'll properly give you your appearance fee...
